<p>For our last meal of 2015, I contributed dal and rotis. This is my first attempt at making either one of these. Both recipes based on Anupy Singla's <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/Indian-Everyone-Anupy-Singla/dp/1572841621">Indian for Everyone</a>.</p>
